WEBVTT

00:02.536 --> 00:04.019
Billy is a puppy.

00:05.088 --> 00:08.084
He lives in a big house with a blue roof.

00:09.131 --> 00:11.319
He loves to play fetch with Emmy.

00:12.408 --> 00:13.823
Emmy throws the ball.

00:14.881 --> 00:16.103
Billy chases it.

00:17.145 --> 00:18.980
Then, Billy sees Cat.

00:19.944 --> 00:22.577
He drops the ball and chases Cat.

00:23.525 --> 00:27.057
Cat runs down the street, and Billy chases him.

00:28.193 --> 00:29.235
Emmy cries,...

00:29.690 --> 00:31.137
..."Come back, Billy."

00:32.158 --> 00:35.637
Cat runs through a farm, and Billy chases him.

00:36.716 --> 00:40.189
Cat runs into the forest, and Billy chases him.

00:41.259 --> 00:43.069
Cat climbs up a tree.

00:43.885 --> 00:47.465
He cannot see the big house with a blue roof.

00:48.193 --> 00:50.828
"Oh, no, I am lost."

00:51.195 --> 00:52.230
Billy says.

00:53.275 --> 00:54.859
Billy runs down a path.

00:55.925 --> 00:57.097
He sees Fox.

00:58.178 --> 00:59.585
"How can I get home?"

01:00.112 --> 01:01.315
He asks Fox.

01:02.313 --> 01:04.319
"I have never been out of the forest."

01:04.834 --> 01:05.899
Says Fox.

01:06.882 --> 01:08.995
"Ask Cow in the farmer's field."

01:09.407 --> 01:10.535
Fox says.

01:11.537 --> 01:13.598
Billy runs to the farmer's field.

01:14.645 --> 01:16.017
Billy says to Cow,...

01:16.476 --> 01:17.734
"I am lost."

01:18.745 --> 01:20.573
"Do you know the way to my house?"

01:21.127 --> 01:22.235
Billy asks.

01:23.281 --> 01:25.863
"I have never been off the farm."

01:26.279 --> 01:27.135
Says Cow.

01:28.189 --> 01:29.587
"Ask Owl."

01:30.024 --> 01:30.914
Cow says.

01:31.981 --> 01:34.144
Billy goes to Owl in the barn.

01:35.199 --> 01:36.689
"Please wake up, Owl."

01:37.169 --> 01:37.985
Says Billy.

01:39.015 --> 01:40.151
"I need your help."

01:40.551 --> 01:41.344
He says.

01:42.414 --> 01:43.633
"I am lost!"

01:44.065 --> 01:44.983
He cries.

01:46.057 --> 01:48.859
"Do you know a big house with a blue roof?"

01:49.279 --> 01:50.174
Billy asks.

01:51.252 --> 01:53.002
"Yes, I do."

01:53.347 --> 01:54.349
Owl says.

01:55.435 --> 01:58.000
Owl flies, and Billy chases her.

01:59.077 --> 02:03.569
Then, Billy sees Emmy at the big house with a blue roof.

02:04.521 --> 02:05.845
"Thank you, Owl."

02:06.281 --> 02:07.307
Says Billy.

